description:
The article details the series of disappearances involving succubi.
There are no commonalities among the victims, and five have vanished
over the course of two months. Whether it's a planned crime or a mere
coincidence remains a question as the incident gradually fades into
obscurity...
name: Article on the Mysterious Series of Disappearances

description:
This media guideline serves as the foundation to grant high value to
the succubus industry as a new renewable energy source and to garner
full support from the general populace as a future national industry.
The published guidelines do not appear to be intentionally damaged...
name: Succubus First Industry Media Guidelines

description:
These are fragments of documents that were found shredded in the trash
can, marked with a distinctive pattern.
name: Torn Documents

description:
A draft article about the death of a client who used the services of
the succubus industry. It coincides with the issuance of the media
guidelines and seems to have been rejected for publication. Despite
the date being quite old, it was found tucked away in a drawer corner.
It is written that the client died from having their life force
drained excessively during sexual intercourse.
name: Article on the Death of a Client Using Succubus First Industry Services

description:
A document entrusted by an employee of a logistics company for
transmission. It seems that it should not be opened...
name: Requested Documents

description:
An apparatus instructed to be worn by employees at a research
institution. It's so customized to one's body that it gives
goosebumps...
name: Suspicious Device

description:
A report found at a research institution. It suggests that the more
succubi become dependent on vital energy, the more they also become
dependent on men. This is thought to be because succubi have
historically been used as consumables.
name: Succubus Essence Dependency Analysis Report

description:
A mysterious disk found in a computer exchanged at a research
institution. A player is needed. There is nothing written on its
surface.
name: Disk

description:
Accusation materials for an insolent new employee. It documents the
unfair treatment they received at the succubus industry.
name: Accusation Materials

description:
A box found at a research institution containing a virus... its
contents are...
name: Box Containing Virus Solution

description:
A box with a biological hazard warning label attached. What is written
cannot be read...
name: Mysterious Box

description:
A key with a unique pattern engraved on it. It has a pattern similar
to that on the <torn document>.
name: Key with a Pattern Drawn on It

description: A card key found at a logistics company. Its purpose is unknown.
name: Card Key

description:
A map detailing the city's water supply facilities. What could this be
used for...?
name: Map of the Water Supply Facility

description:
Documents containing all information regarding the city's water supply
facilities' equipment. What could this be used for...?
name: Water Supply Facility Equipment Documents

description:
A business card of a demon race that seems familiar. There is a
distinctive scar on the face...
name: Familiar Demon's Business Card

description:
Documents containing information about a demon race that seems
familiar. The details are unclear, but it appears to list their past
deeds and experiences.
name: Familiar Demon's Documents

description:
Mysterious documents. They contain coordinates to a specific location
and list of preparation items with unclear serial numbers.
name: Mysterious Documents

description:
Documents about specific coordinates and preparation items required.
They list serial numbers for handcuffs and rope found in a cabinet.

P337187.
name: Handcuffs

A rope found in a security company's cabinet. It is marked with
P409420.

institution. Data collection has been completed.
